Text: Biggest lie I tell myself: EvErYtHiNg WiLl Be BeTtEr OnCe Im ThIn.  Shes a dirty liar that part of my brain.

Author: warmcorgi53
Text: I can relate. When I was overweight, I would refuse to go to formal dances, parties, etc because of how shitty I felt. I always regretted it in the end. Go out. Have fun. You will look back on those days and deeply regret missing out on life experiences. You have nothing to lose
